"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## [Announcing the first Mines of Dalarnia Land Sale!](https://minesofdalarnia.medium.com/announcing-the-first-mines-of-dalarnia-land-sale-ac49214adb5d?source=user_profile---------1-------------------------------)\\n\\n[![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*mjH3DxgK_a6uSvnG1i4isQ.gif)](https://minesofdalarnia.medium.com/announcing-the-first-mines-of-dalarnia-land-sale-ac49214adb5d?source=user_profile---------1-------------------------------)\\n\\n[Mines of Dalarnia](https://www.minesofdalarnia.com/) Land Sale\\n\\nWe are pleased to report that we have finalized the details and dates for the very first **Mining Plot Sale.** The portal will interact with Binance Smart Chain blockchain. The only officially supported wallet for the land sale is **Metamask**. Please prepare by familiarizing yourself with Metamask.\\n\\n## **Important details at a glance:**\\n\\n*   The [land sale…](https://landsale.minesofdalarnia.com/)\\n\\n## [Mines of Dalarnia November Recap](https://minesofdalarnia.medium.com/mines-of-dalarnia-november-recap-a0ec7a1841a2?source=user_profile---------4-------------------------------)\\n\\n[![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*GZfWVuoStdnoBEhlEGdJng.gif)](https://minesofdalarnia.medium.com/mines-of-dalarnia-november-recap-a0ec7a1841a2?source=user_profile---------4-------------------------------)\\n\\nNovember Recap [Mines of Dalarnia](https://www.minesofdalarnia.com/)\\n\\n## Greetings, Miners!\\n\\nNovember was a very busy month full of exciting news, development, and events. To keep the community up to speed, here is a recap of all of these things in one convenient list:\\n\\n*   On November 1st, we reached 48,000 testnet players\\n*   On November 1–2nd, we held a successful IFO on…\\n\\n## [Introducing the $80m Metaverse Grant Program](https://minesofdalarnia.medium.com/introducing-the-80m-metaverse-grant-program-9c6acb732deb?source=user_profile---------7-------------------------------)\\n\\n[![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*RMG-oF5dqtKvxs2kkQCFcw.gif)](https://minesofdalarnia.medium.com/introducing-the-80m-metaverse-grant-program-9c6acb732deb?source=user_profile---------7-------------------------------)\\n\\n[Mines of Dalarnia](https://www.minesofdalarnia.com/)\\n\\n**Founded in collaboration with Chromia and My Neighbor Alice, the $80m program will provide support to the most promising ideas in an effort to expand the metaverse surrounding Mines of Dalarnia and the Chromia ecosystem at large.**\\n\\nThe P2E action adventure game Mines of Dalarnia is quickly gaining traction in…[](https://twitter.com/MinesOfDalarnia/status/1456266911235248151?s=20)[](https://minesofdalarnia.medium.com/take-a-peek-at-mines-of-dalarnia-2-0-spoiler-alert-4b121a7a5472)\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640874978,\"title\":\"Mines of Dalarnia – Medium\"},\"digest\":\"VHTpwXr0mZSir2FAlpo1x6xvVNIK8o-BWjfe4QbPXMU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x6Acf04cD3c60aF7893F44E88F3ef3b413A985594\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"rPKvnPCoeO-QtDtlCqLehmCTNnjSgo1zdSTZeeeETQY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"5Y5gzzvZnX8O2cIL27WYFM6Fr8kQMmEPNLfh1NuXo3k\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"xcXs8_YUSTF_I2cTORsn7xABBJ0XhoHQM0xaxNg5eyvjXbvWRq4_Lum0BqYKc8qMgBkIJiAvls7Zwa1Awi0h5g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe9a566c3b7ba651f840766f0c3dac77829596cd2e057474a4a390d78f4aff6634d17395b03fd5dba7d51a88ad996b556b10812d148ffd694edb5ddbdec9664411c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"rPKvnPCoeO-QtDtlCqLehmCTNnjSgo1zdSTZeeeETQY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"5Y5gzzvZnX8O2cIL27WYFM6Fr8kQMmEPNLfh1NuXo3k\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"VHTpwXr0mZSir2FAlpo1x6xvVNIK8o-BWjfe4QbPXMU\"}"